Java8 or above needed for gradle

Download java 8 (JDK8):
========================

https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/downloads/#java8

Windows x64 Installer

1. download .exe (java8) file and execute on specific folder on pc.

add environment variable as --> on windows --> advanced system setting --> env variables -->on system variables 
click on new and add 

JAVA_HOME
C:\Devops_softwares\jdk8\bin   

and add path:
C:\Devops_softwares\jdk8\  --> Save and check


